snippet.title: Rival Peak - Official Reveal Trailer (Survivor + Social Media Game)
snippet.description:
Check out the reveal trailer for Rival Peak, the Survivor-style video game show on Facebook where players watch AI-controlled players 24/7 and help manipulate the game-within-the-game to see who will be voted off next. Rival Peak launches on December 2 at 6:30pm PT.

#ign
